---
title: Braised Chicken and Mushrooms with Buttery Smashed Potatoes
description: Here comes the flavours of a slow-cooked homemade supper, in a fraction of the time! Savoury mushrooms make this tender chicken dish taste like it's been bubbling away on the stove all day.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-et-champignons-braises-ca4d89e4.jpg
